@developer @contribution
Feature: Developer Contribution Experience
  As a developer
  I want to understand and contribute to the framework
  So that I can help build effective educational tools

  Background:
    Given I am a developer interested in contributing
    And I have accessed the framework documentation

  @wip
  Scenario: Understand project structure
    When I view the main documentation
    Then I should see a clear project overview
    And I should understand the component architecture
    And I should see contribution guidelines

  @wip
  Scenario: Access technical setup documentation
    Given I want to set up a development environment
    When I follow the technical setup guide
    Then I should see clear installation instructions
    And I should understand the development workflow
    And I should be able to run the local development server

  @wip
  Scenario: Find contribution opportunities
    Given I want to contribute to the project
    When I explore the contribution areas
    Then I should see clearly defined areas needing development
    And I should understand how to get started
    And I should find beginner-friendly tasks
